    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Magic Bean</strong></h2>This is the ultimate test of skill and determination : 🫘<strong>Magic Bean</strong>🍃 , an intense platformer❕<br><br>Each level is designed to push the limits of your abilities, with precision timing and quick <br>reflexes required to overcome the obstacles in your path. With mind-bending level design, and increasing difficulty, <br>Magic Bean will keep you on the edge of your seat as you strive to reach new heights. <br><br>This game is only for the players looking for a real chalenge, it's super hard and there is no mercy❕⚔️💀<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climbing</strong></h2><br>In Magic Bean you have to jump from platform to platform to reach the next stage, but be careful: if you fall you have to start again, so don't confuse speed with precipitation !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/97e7799ee59b99908b7605dab3e6881c.poster.avif?t=1698426161\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/97e7799ee59b99908b7605dab3e6881c.webm?t=1698426161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/97e7799ee59b99908b7605dab3e6881c.mp4?t=1698426161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade</strong></h2><br>You can unlock teleporters, buy tools, improve them and improve your character.<br>Choose wisely, because your choices can greatly influence your success.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/74334fef874d45afcd9a47029ce3089b.poster.avif?t=1698426161\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/74334fef874d45afcd9a47029ce3089b.webm?t=1698426161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/74334fef874d45afcd9a47029ce3089b.mp4?t=1698426161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tools</strong></h2><br>There are tools that are like skills that can be unlocked and can be a great help in your climb.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/f9bb0a2a978b2b7877e7c1ce044a5add.poster.avif?t=1698426161\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/f9bb0a2a978b2b7877e7c1ce044a5add.webm?t=1698426161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346980/extras/f9bb0a2a978b2b7877e7c1ce044a5add.mp4?t=1698426161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hard Challenge</strong></h2><strong>Good luck, you will need it</strong>❗",
